name: Test Scene Jump
description:
You jump from the church tower and manage to land on both your feet at the same time. However, your momentum wants to have a talk with the ground and continues to travel towards it, despite the best efforts of your muscles. With several sickening crunches your body comes to a rest on the ground.

On the bright side you don't care about those noises. You don't care about anything anymore. Because you're dead.

THE END
